---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Icon from '../components/Icon.astro';

const schema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'WebPage',
  name: 'Our Methodology - How We Evaluate Services',
  description: 'Learn about our transparent, evidence-based methodology for comparing men\'s health telehealth services.',
};
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Our Methodology - How We Compare Services"
  description="Transparent, evidence-based methodology for evaluating and comparing men's health telehealth services. Learn how we research, test, and review."
  schema={schema}
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-white py-12 lg:py-16 border-b border-slate-200">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-600 mb-6">
          <a href="/" class="hover:text-brand-accent transition-colors">Home</a>
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-slate-900 font-medium">Methodology</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 sm:mb-6 leading-tight px-4">
          Our Methodology
        </h1>
        <p class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4">
          How we evaluate, compare, and present information about men's health telehealth services.
          Transparency matters—here's exactly how we work.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Core Principles -->
  <section class="section bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8 text-center">
        Our Core Principles
      </h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="card p-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <Icon name="target" class="w-6 h-6" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3 text-slate-900">No Rankings</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            We don't rank services as "best overall" because there is no universal winner. Instead, we identify
            which service is "best for" specific needs—best for price, best for variety, best for speed, etc.
            Your priorities determine the best choice for you.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card p-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-600 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <Icon name="search" class="w-6 h-6" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3 text-slate-900">Evidence-Based</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            All medical information comes from peer-reviewed research, clinical guidelines, and expert consensus.
            We cite sources and link to original research. Claims without evidence are clearly labeled as such.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card p-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-amber-100 text-amber-600 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <Icon name="affordability" class="w-6 h-6" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3 text-slate-900">Transparent Affiliations</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            We use affiliate links and may earn commissions when you purchase through our links. This is disclosed
            on every page. Crucially, affiliate relationships do NOT influence our comparisons—we present all
            services equally and let you decide.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card p-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-purple-100 text-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <Icon name="weight-loss" class="w-6 h-6" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3 text-slate-900">Balanced Perspective</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            Every service has pros and cons. We present both honestly. We don't hide negative aspects or
            exaggerate positives. Our goal is to give you the complete picture so you can make an informed decision.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Evaluation Process -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 text-center">
        Our Evaluation Process
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-10 text-center">
        How we research and evaluate each telehealth service
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand-accent/10 text-brand-accent flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xl">
              1
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2 text-slate-900">Initial Research</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">
              We start by thoroughly researching each service: reviewing their website, terms of service,
              privacy policy, pricing structure, available treatments, and medical team credentials.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-1">
              <li>• Review official website and documentation</li>
              <li>• Verify physician licensing and credentials</li>
              <li>• Document all pricing and fees</li>
              <li>• Identify unique features and limitations</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand-accent/10 text-brand-accent flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xl">
              2
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2 text-slate-900">User Experience Testing</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">
              Where possible, we go through the actual consultation process to evaluate user experience,
              customer service, shipping times, and product quality.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-1">
              <li>• Test signup and consultation process</li>
              <li>• Evaluate website usability and mobile experience</li>
              <li>• Measure response times and customer support</li>
              <li>• Assess packaging and delivery quality</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand-accent/10 text-brand-accent flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xl">
              3
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2 text-slate-900">Review Aggregation</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">
              We analyze thousands of user reviews from multiple sources to identify common themes, complaints,
              and praise. This gives us insight into real-world experiences.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-1">
              <li>• Aggregate reviews from Trustpilot, Google, Reddit, and forums</li>
              <li>• Identify recurring positive and negative themes</li>
              <li>• Verify complaint patterns and resolution</li>
              <li>• Monitor BBB ratings and complaints</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand-accent/10 text-brand-accent flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xl">
              4
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2 text-slate-900">Medical Accuracy Review</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">
              All medical information is fact-checked against peer-reviewed literature, clinical guidelines,
              and FDA resources. We consult with medical professionals when needed.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-1">
              <li>• Cross-reference claims with medical literature</li>
              <li>• Verify medication information with FDA databases</li>
              <li>• Consult clinical practice guidelines</li>
              <li>• Review for potential misinformation</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand-accent/10 text-brand-accent flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xl">
              5
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2 text-slate-900">Ongoing Monitoring</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">
              Telehealth services change frequently. We monitor pricing updates, new features, policy changes,
              and user feedback to keep our content accurate.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-1">
              <li>• Monthly pricing verification</li>
              <li>• Quarterly deep reviews of each service</li>
              <li>• Real-time monitoring of major changes</li>
              <li>• Continuous user feedback collection</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Comparison Criteria -->
  <section class="section-light">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 text-center">
        What We Evaluate
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-10 text-center">
        Key factors we consider when comparing services
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="card p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-3 text-slate-900 flex items-center gap-2">
            <Icon name="affordability" class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-600" />
            Cost & Value
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <li>• Consultation fees (or lack thereof)</li>
            <li>• Medication pricing (monthly/per-dose)</li>
            <li>• Hidden fees and shipping costs</li>
            <li>• Insurance acceptance and FSA/HSA eligibility</li>
            <li>• Subscription requirements and flexibility</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-3 text-slate-900 flex items-center gap-2">
            <Icon name="doctor" class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600" />
            Medical Quality
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <li>• Physician credentials and licensing</li>
            <li>• Quality of medical consultation</li>
            <li>• Medication options (brand vs. generic vs. compounded)</li>
            <li>• Follow-up care and ongoing monitoring</li>
            <li>• Evidence-based treatment protocols</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-3 text-slate-900 flex items-center gap-2">
            <Icon name="phone" class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-600" />
            User Experience
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <li>• Ease of signup and consultation process</li>
            <li>• Website and mobile app quality</li>
            <li>• Customer service responsiveness</li>
            <li>• Prescription refill process</li>
            <li>• Account management and flexibility</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-3 text-slate-900 flex items-center gap-2">
            <Icon name="zap" class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600" />
            Speed & Convenience
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <li>• Time to approval</li>
            <li>• Shipping speed and tracking</li>
            <li>• Discreet packaging</li>
            <li>• Availability of expedited options</li>
            <li>• Auto-refill and subscription management</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-3 text-slate-900 flex items-center gap-2">
            <Icon name="privacy" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-600" />
            Privacy & Security
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <li>• HIPAA compliance</li>
            <li>• Data security practices</li>
            <li>• Discreet billing and packaging</li>
            <li>• Privacy policy transparency</li>
            <li>• Third-party data sharing</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-3 text-slate-900 flex items-center gap-2">
            <Icon name="transparency" class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-600" />
            Reputation & Trust
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <li>• User review averages across platforms</li>
            <li>• BBB rating and complaint resolution</li>
            <li>• Years in operation</li>
            <li>• Company transparency and ethics</li>
            <li>• Response to negative feedback</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Limitations -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 text-center">
        Our Limitations
      </h2>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          We believe in transparency about what we can and cannot do:
        </p>

        <div class="card p-6 mb-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-slate-900">We are not medical professionals</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            While we research medical topics thoroughly and cite clinical evidence, we are not doctors.
            Our content is for informational purposes only and does not constitute medical advice.
            Always consult a qualified healthcare provider for medical decisions.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card p-6 mb-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-slate-900">We cannot verify all user reviews</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            While we aggregate reviews from multiple sources, we cannot independently verify every review's
            authenticity. We note patterns and trends rather than relying on individual reviews.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card p-6 mb-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-slate-900">Pricing can change frequently</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Telehealth services update their pricing regularly. While we monitor changes monthly, there may
            be brief periods where our listed prices are outdated. We always recommend verifying current
            pricing directly with the service.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-slate-900">Affiliate relationships exist</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            We earn commissions from affiliate links. While we strive to remain objective, this creates
            a potential conflict of interest. We mitigate this by presenting all services equally and
            clearly disclosing our relationships.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Feedback CTA -->
  <section class="section bg-slate-900 text-white">
    <div class="container-custom text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">
        Help Us Improve
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-6">
        Found an error? Have feedback on our methodology? We want to hear from you.
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="mailto:feedback@comparemenscare.com" class="btn bg-white text-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-100">
          Send Feedback
        </a>
        <a href="/about" class="btn-outline border-white text-white hover:bg-white/10">
          About Us
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
